room_title: Escape room "The Crash" by Escape Key in Tallahassee
room_address: 501 E Tennessee St, Suite D, Tallahassee, FL, 32308
room_description: The world is descending into chaos as the internet is shutting down across the globe. Your group is approached by a mysterious stranger who offers you an opportunity to save the world by entering the digital realm. You have 60 minutes to find the source bringing the system to a halt and save the world, or be stuck in the system forever.
